@Comment:	Time is 4:36
@Comment:	Date: March 12 , 1993. Hi Julie , I miss you. Come back soon. Please write back. I wish you were here. Love , Chi (full name , in script)
@Comment:	MOT suggests that Chi write to Chi's former teacher who has moved out of state. Chi is fine with this idea. Chi generally writes independently and competently. She asks Mot for help when needed. Mot lets Chi generate the text , but keeps a watchful eye on Chi's spelling and puncuation. Mot seems supportive and very proud of Chi's accomplishments. I get the feeling that Mot would have had more input into the content of the letter if not for Sis's interruptions.
